data.description: Large 4 bedroom home with mother-in-law addition. Plenty of room for everyone in this house. Large living room with fireplace. Mother-in-law addition measures 23x20 with private bathroom. Not included in the 2,301 sq. footage is a 16x16 3 seasons room on back with skylights. There is an att. garage plus a 24x20 det. for all the big toys or a great workshop. City water. Large front and back yard. Not far from Lake Huron and 3 mile park.
